{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, like maybe at that point, it was like 30 or 40 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I entered the crowd and I listened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were talking about that the house in the distance which they saw, which was across a wall, which was a house inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They saw Jewish women throwing themselves with children from the upper floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was-- I did not see that picture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were recounting that picture, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that's the only other thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then one more incident, after the uprising which finished in May, as I walked once on the street, I suddenly saw two people emerge like from a sewer, you know, from a-- you could see a deck lifted.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were running for their life someplace, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I saw that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Which fits the stories, which you subsequently read about the ghetto, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I did not have any contact, or I didn't fight in the ghettos, or no way, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I dreamt, I wished I could have done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what could I have done?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's nothing I could have done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have armaments.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have a gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't have connections anywhere to buy a gun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know how to even enter the ghetto, if I wanted to do that, which would have been suicidal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, you know, even if I wanted to do that, there was no way I could do that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not see-- you see, the ghetto was cordoned off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I didn't even know how to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would not-- haven't been born in Warsaw, and only living eight months, I didn't know enough of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
